Package org.elasticsearch.transport.client

Class PreBuiltTransportClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.common.component.AbstractComponent
      • org.elasticsearch.client.support.AbstractClient
        • org.elasticsearch.client.transport.TransportClient
          • org.elasticsearch.transport.client.PreBuiltTransportClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, Client, ElasticsearchClient, Releasable

    public class PreBuiltTransportClient
extends TransportClient
    A builder to create an instance of TransportClient. This class pre-installs the Netty4Plugin, ReindexPlugin, PercolatorPlugin, MustachePlugin, ParentJoinPlugin plugins for the client. These plugins are all the required modules for Elasticsearch. Note that TransportClient will be deprecated in Elasticsearch 7.0 and removed in Elasticsearch 8.0. Use the High Level REST Client instead.
